LAUNCH program with:
ppython main.py
(requires panda3D SDK)

CAMERA CONTROL (PERSPECTIVAL CHANGES):
TAB - toggle free camera
Mouse - move camera
Z - Move camera
Q - Move camera
S - Move camera
D - Move camera
T - go up
G - go down

E - go to and follow earth
R - go to and follow moon
F - go to and follow sun

control-E - look at earth
control-R - look at moon
control-F - look at sun

A - stop following
W - stop looking at

FACTUAL CHANGES:
shift-E	to toggle earth tilt
shift-R to toggle moon inclination

TIME CONTROL:
L - Speed x 2
K - Speed / 2
I - Inverse speed
N - start/stop flow of  time
